    <div class="col-xs-10 col-xs-offset-1">
      <p class="notice"><%= notice %></p>
      <p class="alert"><%= alert %></p>
    </div>

    <div class="col-xs-10 col-xs-offset-1 centered">
      <h1 class="bottom-margin">Welcome to Wolf Lacrosse</h1>
      <div class="col-xs-7">
        <p class="justify">Wolf Lacrosse is a one-of-a-kind lacrosse experience for young players that specializes on player positions and development. At Wolf Lacrosse Camps, you will improve your lacrosse IQ, skills, fundamentals, and work ethic through a highly structured and efficient lacrosse program. Our goals are very simple. We want every player to improve his skills and become more proficient AND we want every player to have a blast playing the sport of lacrosse!  Please note that our camps are designed for boys in or entering grade 4 and above.</p>
